data.text:
Directions

From CT- Take CT-262 and merge onto CT-8 South toward Waterbury. Take exit 33 to merge onto I-84 West toward Danbury. Follow exit 20 for I-684 toward NY-22 / White Plains / Pawling. Keep left at the fork to continue toward I-684 South and merge onto I-684 South. Merge onto Hutchinson River Pkwy South. Continue onto Cross County Pkwy. Then take the Saw Mill Pkwy South exit toward New York City. Merge onto Saw Mill River Pkwy. Continue onto Henry Hudson Pkwy. Take the exit toward 79th St / Boat Basin. At the traffic circle, take second exit onto W 79th St. Turn left onto Amsterdam Ave. Take second right onto W 81st St. Continue onto 79th Street Transverse Rd. Turn right on 5th Ave until you reach East 61st Street. The 800B entrance is on 5th Avenue between 61st and 62nd Streets. New York Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery Dental Implant Center will be on your left.

From NJ- Merge onto I-95 West via the ramp to Trenton. Take exit 6 for New Jersey Turnpike. Keep left at the fork and continue toward I-95 North / New Jersey Turnpike North. Take exit 16 E toward Lincoln Tunnel / NJ-3. Keep left at the fork. Follow signs for NJ-3 / Secaucus and merge onto NJ-495 East. Continue onto Lincoln Tunnel. Take the exit toward West 40th Street. Turn right at West 40th Street. Turn left at the 2nd cross street onto 8th Ave. At the traffic circle, take the 3rd exit onto Central Park West. Turn right onto 65th Street Transverse Rd. Take the second right onto 5th Ave. Proceed on 5th Avenue until you reach East 61st Street. The 800B entrance is on 5th Avenue between 61st and 62nd Streets. New York Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery Dental Implant Center will be on your left.

From LI- Take I-495 West / New York. Take exit 42 for Northern Parkway West toward New York. Merge onto Northern State Parkway and continue onto Grand Central Parkway West. Exit onto Union Turnpike. Turn right at Queens Blvd. Continue onto Queensboro Bridge. Turn left on 63rd St. Turn left on 5th Ave. Proceed on 5th Avenue until you reach East 61st Street. The 800B entrance is on 5th Avenue between 61st and 62nd Streets. New York Oral & Maxillofacial Dental Implant Surgery Center will be on your left.
